arg1: no one promises that it won't get rough when you decide to follow your dreams
arg2: the idea is not to quit.
original_utt: you have a point there. i got that too. i liked when the wave knocked moana over though and she wanted to quit and her grandmother encouraged her not to quit. kind of like life. no one promises that it won't get rough when you decide to follow your dreams but the idea is not to quit. keep on pursuing your dreams no matter how difficult it gets.
original_utt_prev: She was cool too but Maui was my favorite. I liked the message that it sent too. That no matter what do not be afraid to do the impossible. Do not be afraid to pursue your dreams.
